ha, I'm glad the translation is working!* 😄\n\nI'll keep responding in English as you requested. Is there anything else you'd like to discuss?\n\n_(qwen3.5 · chat · 14.3s)_\",\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":null,\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":\"💭 *Reasoning:*\nMichelle is asking if she should create a game scenario from Kingdom Guard for us to solve together - I should respond in Bulgarian with English translation as per the translation preference.\n\n*Да, това звучи страхотно!* 🎮\n\nСъздай ситуация от играта и ще се опитаме да я решим заедно. Мога да ти помогна с:\n\n• Анализ на ситуацията\n• Предлагане на решения\n• Обсъждане на различни подходи\n• Препоръки за следващи стъпки\n\nЧакам ситуацията! 🏰\n\n_(qwen3.5+think · chat · 24.4s)_\",\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":null,\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":\"*Да, знам какво е Burning Expedition!* 🔥\n\n**Burning Expedition** е мобилна игра за стратегия и оцеляване, която включва:\n\n**Основни елементи:**\n• Оцеляване в постапокалиптичен свят\n• Събиране на ресурси и изграждане на база\n• Създаване на отряд и битки с врагове\n• Изследване на територии и откриване на тайни\n\n**Игрален процес:**\n• Управляваш отряд оцелели\n• Трябва да се бориш за храна, вода и други ресурси\n• Изграждаш убежище и защитаваш се от врагове\n• Съюзници и альянси са важни за успех\n\nИскате ли да ви дам повече информация за конкретни аспекти на играта? 🎮\n\n_(qwen3.5 · chat · 24.3s)_\",\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":null,\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":\"*Да, знам за Broken Lands в Kingdom Guard!* 🌲\n\n**Broken Lands** е специална зона в Kingdom Guard, която включва:\n\n**Основни елементи:**\n• Изследване на разрушена територия\n• Събиране на уникални ресурси\n• Битки с врагове и бандити\n• Откриване на тайни и награди\n\n**Предимства:**\n• Получавате ексклузивни предмети и герои\n• Увеличавате силата на отряда си\n• Получавате ресурси за развитие на града\n\n**Стратегия:**\n• Изпращайте силен отряд за изследване\n• Бъдете готови за битки по всяко време\n• Вземете ресурсите навреме, преди да се върнете\n\nИскате ли повече информация за конкретни аспекти на Broken Lands? 🗺️\n\n_(qwen3.5 · chat · 22.4s)_\",\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":null,\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":\"💭 *Reasoning:*\nThe preferences show translator_languages is set to ['en'], so I should explain that the translation system is configured correctly and ask Michelle to clarify what she's experiencing.\n\n*The translation settings show that English is enabled for translation.* 📋\n\nThe system is configured to translate responses to English when the response isn't in English. However, I notice that Michelle's messages are in Bulgarian, and I'm responding in Bulgarian.\n\n**The translation feature works like this:**\n- When Michelle sends a message in Bulgarian, I respond in Bulgarian\n- When you (DJ) ask for translation, I should respond in English\n- The translation preference is set to translate to English\n\n**What's happening:**\n- Michelle's messages are in Bulgarian, so I respond in Bulgarian\n- The translation preference doesn't automatically translate my Bulgarian responses to English for you\n\n**To fix this:**\nIf you want all responses to be in English regardless of what language Michelle uses, I can set a preference for that. Would you like me to do that? 🤔\n\n_(qwen3.5+think · chat · 28.3s)_\",\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":null,\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":\"*You're absolutely right!* My previous response was already in English, so it didn't need translation.\n\n**How the translation system works:**\n- When Michelle sends a message in Bulgarian, I respond in Bulgarian\n- The translation preference translates responses *to* English when needed\n- If I respond in English, no translation is needed\n\n**The confusion:**\n- I was responding in Bulgarian to Michelle's Bulgarian messages\n- When you asked about translation, I explained in English (no translation needed)\n- The system is working correctly - it just translates responses to the subscribed languages\n\n**What would you like?**\n- Keep responses in English regardless of input language?\n- Or continue with the current behavior (respond in the language of the message)?\n\nLet me know and I can adjust the preferences accordingly! 🎯\n\n_(qwen3.5 · chat · 23.5s)_\",\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":null,\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":\"💭 *Reasoning:*\nThe preference was set successfully, so I should confirm the change and explain how the translation system will now work for both incoming requests and responses.\n\n✅ **Translation preference updated!**\n\n**Now the system will:**\n- Translate Michelle's Bulgarian requests to English for processing\n- Translate my responses back to Bulgarian for Michelle\n- Keep responses in English when the request is already in English\n\n**This means:**\n- Michelle sends a message in Bulgarian → I see it translated to English → I respond in English → Michelle sees it translated back to Bulgarian\n- DJ sends a message in English → I see it in English → I respond in English (no translation needed)\n\nThe translation system is now configured to handle both directions! 🌐\n\n_(qwen3.5+think · chat · 27.9s)_\",\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":null,\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":\"*Здравей, Michelle!* 👋\n\nКак мога да ти помогна днес?\n\n_(qwen3.5 · chat · 13.9s)_\",\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_START---\n{\"status\":\"success\",\"result\":null,\"newSessionId\":\"ollama-1773997756692\"}\n---NANOCLAW_OUTPUT_END---\n"
